name: BTV Frequencies 003 - Case Num. POTG-3009
description: Beyond the Void series by RocketSpaceboy. The BTV Frequencies work examines the frequencies received in the interdimensional existence beyond space and time. This specific piece is part of the Frequencies Collection.  Sometimes the frequencies from the Beyond penetrate our small part of the Universe. In doing so we often find unexplainable nightmares which occupy not only our dreams but also our realities. Such is the case with Case Number: POTG-3009
